│ the IR is split into two versions (`.us` and default) and the load may be   │
│ conditionally executed. The SCEV for `%v` remains the same (as a            │
│ `scUnknown`), but its dominance relationship to loop `%loop1` changes       │
│ because the load's block may not dominate the loop header in the new        │
